00:27:23,866 --> 00:27:31,390
nitpicking about it. Two, uh we designed our heuristics the way we did specifically to

506
00:27:31,390 --> 00:27:38,915
avoid people gaming the system. So all of the kind of branching decisions in our game, all

507
00:27:38,915 --> 00:27:45,718
of the ways relationships can grow are written from this baseline kind of design

